@page "/about"

<PageTitle>About - PdfToolStack</PageTitle>

<HeadContent>
    <meta name="description" content="About PdfToolStack: practical, privacy-minded tools for compressing, converting, signing, organizing, securing, and reviewing PDFs." />
    <link rel="canonical" href="https://pdftoolstack.com/about" />
</HeadContent>

<main class="trust-page">
    <section class="trust-hero">
        <div>
            <span class="trust-eyebrow">About PdfToolStack</span>
            <h1>PDF workflows that stay practical.</h1>
            <p>
                PdfToolStack is being built to make common document work faster: compressing,
                converting, signing, organizing, securing, and reviewing PDFs without heavy desktop
                software.
            </p>
        </div>
        <aside class="trust-summary-card">
            <span>Product focus</span>
            <strong>Useful tools, clear limits, privacy-minded defaults.</strong>
            <small>No invented company story. No unsupported legal claims.</small>
        </aside>
    </section>

    <section class="trust-grid">
        <article class="trust-card">
            <h2>What we are building</h2>
            <p>
                PdfToolStack combines everyday PDF utilities with selected AI-assisted workflows.
                The goal is to help users complete document tasks with less friction while keeping
                expectations clear.
            </p>
        </article>

        <article class="trust-card">
            <h2>Trust basics</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Uploaded files are intended for temporary processing.</li>
                <li>Files are designed to be deleted automatically after processing, typically within 1 hour.</li>
                <li>We do not intentionally keep permanent copies of uploaded documents.</li>
                <li>Users should review generated files before relying on them.</li>
            </ul>
        </article>

        <article class="trust-card">
            <h2>Who it is for</h2>
            <p>
                PdfToolStack is for individuals, small teams, operations staff, finance teams,
                HR teams, legal-adjacent workflows, and anyone who regularly needs to fix, convert,
                reduce, sign, or organize documents.
            </p>
        </article>

        <article class="trust-card">
            <h2>Where we are careful</h2>
            <p>
                PDF and AI workflows can make mistakes. PdfToolStack is not a substitute for
                professional review, legal advice, financial advice, or human judgment when the
                document matters.
            </p>
        </article>

        <article class="trust-card">
            <h2>Questions</h2>
            <p>
                For product, privacy, billing, or support questions, contact:
            </p>
            <a class="trust-inline-link" href="mailto:admin@pdftoolstack.com">admin@pdftoolstack.com</a>
        </article>

        <article class="trust-card">
            <h2>Business details placeholder</h2>
            <p class="trust-placeholder">
                Placeholder: add verified legal entity name, business address, registered agent,
                tax details, and final policy review before using these pages as final legal terms.
            </p>
        </article>
    </section>
</main>
